<h1>Frankie Flowers</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://frankieflowersmusic.com/now/">frankieflowersmusic.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Milwaukee
WI
United States
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Singer/songwriter and the owner of Frankly Beautiful Creations, LLC which serves as a music hub for publishing through BMI.
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I create stories from the experiences of myself and others, and put them into songs.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
My mom has lupus and said one day my stories will impact the world in a way beyond my imagination. She said I am the voice for the voiceless through the songs I write. I just want to give hope to a generation of kids feeling like giving up on life.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
It takes 30 days to make or break a habit. If you seek to add more positivity in your life then you must do so by living in accordance with this principle.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
<p>
The Millionaire Fastlane by MJ DeMarco
</p>

